<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="th">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>ทายผลบอลโลก World Cup 2026</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Prompt:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root { --bg: #f8fafc; --surface: #ffffff; --text: #0f172a; --text-muted: #64748b; --primary: #2563eb; --primary-hover: #1d4ed8; --border: #e2e8f0; }
        body { font-family: 'Prompt', sans-serif; background-color: var(--bg); color: var(--text); margin: 0; padding: 20px; }
        .container { max-width: 1000px; margin: 0 auto; }
        .header-card { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e293b, #0f172a); color: white; border-radius: 16px; padding: 20px 30px; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 30px; box-shadow: 0 10px 15px -3px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.1); }
        .user-info { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 15px; }
        .user-info img { width: 56px; height: 56px; border-radius: 50%; object-fit: cover; border: 3px solid #38bdf8; background: #fff; }
        .user-info h3 { margin: 0; font-size: 1.2rem; }
        .user-info p { margin: 0; color: #94a3b8; font-size: 0.9rem; }
        .nav-links a { color: white; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 500; margin-left: 20px; transition: color 0.2s; }
        .nav-links a:hover { color: #38bdf8; } .nav-links a.admin-link { color: #86efac; } .nav-links a.logout-link { color: #fca5a5; }
        .card { background: var(--surface); border-radius: 16px; padding: 24px; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.05); border: 1px solid var(--border); }
        .card-title { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: flex-end; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .card-title h2 { margin: 0; color: var(--text); font-size: 1.5rem; }
        table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; }
        th, td { padding: 16px; text-align: left; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
        th { background-color: var(--bg); font-weight: 600; color: var(--text-muted); }
        .team-name { font-weight: 600; font-size: 1.05rem; }
        .vs { color: var(--text-muted); margin: 0 8px; font-size: 0.9rem; }
        input[type="number"] { width: 60px; padding: 8px; border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 8px; text-align: center; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; }
        input[type="number"]:focus { outline: none; border-color: var(--primary); }
        input:disabled { background-color: #f1f5f9; color: #94a3b8; cursor: not-allowed; }
        .btn { padding: 8px 16px; background-color: var(--primary); color: white; border: none; border-radius: 8px; font-family: inherit; font-weight: 500; cursor: pointer; transition: 0.2s; text-decoration: none; display: inline-block;}
        .btn:hover { background-color: var(--primary-hover); }
        .btn-view { background-color: #10b981; } .btn-view:hover { background-color: #059669; }
        .locked-badge { color: #94a3b8; font-size: 0.9rem; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 5px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header-card">
            <div class="user-info">
                <img src="<%= user.avatar %>" alt="Avatar">
                <div><p>ยินดีต้อนรับ</p><h3><%= user.username %></h3></div>
            </div>
            <div class="nav-links">
                <a href="/leaderboard">📊 ตารางคะแนนรวม</a>
                <% if(user.is_admin) { %> <a href="/admin" class="admin-link">⚙️ แผงควบคุม (Admin)</a> <% } %>
                <a href="/logout" class="logout-link">ออกจากระบบ</a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <div class="card-title"><h2>🏆 ตารางแข่งขันและการทายผล</h2><small>⏱️ ล็อกผลอัตโนมัติ 5 นาทีก่อนแข่ง</small></div>
            <table>
                <thead><tr><th width="15%">รอบ</th><th width="30%">คู่แข่งขัน</th><th width="15%">ผลจริง</th><th width="25%">การทายผลของคุณ</th><th width="15%">ดูของเพื่อน</th></tr></thead>
                <tbody>
                    <% if(matches.length === 0) { %><tr><td colspan="5" style="text-align: center; padding: 40px; color: var(--text-muted);">ยังไม่มีตารางการแข่งขัน</td></tr><% } %>
                    <% matches.forEach(match => { %>
                        <tr>
                            <td><span style="color: var(--text-muted);"><%= match.stage_name %></span><br><small><%= match.kickoff_time %></small></td>
                            <td><span class="team-name"><%= match.home_team %></span> <span class="vs">vs</span> <span class="team-name"><%= match.away_team %></span></td>
                            <td>
                                <% if(match.status === 'FINISHED') { %> <span style="color: #16a34a; font-weight: 700; font-size: 1.1rem;"><%= match.home_score %> - <%= match.away_score %></span>
                                <% } else { %> <span style="color: var(--text-muted);">-</span> <% } %>
                            </td>
                            <td>
                                <form action="/predict" method="POST" style="margin:0; display:flex; gap:10px; align-items:center;">
                                    <input type="hidden" name="match_id" value="<%= match.id %>">
                                    <input type="number" name="home_predict" value="<%= match.home_predict %>" <% if(match.is_locked) { %>disabled<% } %>> :
                                    <input type="number" name="away_predict" value="<%= match.away_predict %>" <% if(match.is_locked) { %>disabled<% } %>>
                                    <% if(!match.is_locked) { %> <button type="submit" class="btn">บันทึก</button>
                                    <% } else { %> <div class="locked-badge">🔒 ล็อกแล้ว</div> <% } %>
                                </form>
                            </td>
                            <td>
                                <% if(match.is_published) { %>
                                    <a href="/match/<%= match.id %>/predictions" class="btn btn-view">👁️ ดูคำทายเพื่อน</a>
                                <% } else { %>
                                    <small style="color: var(--text-muted);">🔒 รอยืนยัน</small>
                                <% } %>
                            </td>
                        </tr>
                    <% }) %>
                </tbody>
            </table>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>